snippet.title: Mother of Many - Game Jam Trailer
snippet.description:
Available at brainwash-gang.itch.io/mother-of-many

"Far deep into the woods lived a family of mice, there weren't two or three or four but dozens of mouths..."

"Mother of Many" is a horde killing roguelite. Harvest vegetables, make a soup with your older sister and get stronger in order to end your family's curse.

 A Brainwash Gang's internal gamejam game, made by (in no particular order):
Sergio "Pikas" - Jorge Monlongo - Beícoli - Rafer - Bini - Quike Zárraga - Javi "Pinnit" - Marcos "Muffin D. Sepia" - Eva Cid - Carlos Cortés - Edu Verz - Mohammed Bakir Khawam - Marc Sureda - Carlos C. Gurpegui - LeGord - Joel Torrent - Red Forge - Ivan Papiol - Jose María "The Cat Sidhe"
